Game class
----------

This event operates on an instance of the [Game\_class.html game class] type idWeapon

Description
-----------

Set the state of the [Script\_object.html script objects] [Finite\_State\_Machine\_(scripting).html Finite State Machine].

Usage
-----

*void* weaponState( *string* **stateFunction**, *float* **blendFrames** )

Parameters
----------

-   [stateFunction] - Name of the state to set. This is simply the name of a function in the script object.
-   [blendFrames] - Frames of animation to blend over state change.

